    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "$46,900 - Mint overall condition. Runs and drives exactly as it should and presents exceptionally well inside and out. The paint, body, and interior show very minimal wear, and it appears to have been very well cared for. A clean, well-kept example that should need little to nothing beyond routine maintenance.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
