      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Offered for sale is a mint-condition example that presents exceptionally well and stands out as a truly well-kept vehicle. It shows extremely little wear for its age, has the kind of clean, cared-for appearance buyers hope to find, and should appeal to someone looking for a top-tier car rather than a project or average driver. This is not just a usable older vehicle\u2014it is the kind of example that has been preserved and maintained to a very high standard, with strong cosmetics, a very tidy overall presentation, and the feel of a vehicle that has been properly looked after. Buyers can expect a standout car that is far above the norm and suitable for someone who wants one of the better examples available.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward, and priced to move, this vehicle is a great fit for buyers seeking dependable basic transportation or a solid starting point for a hands-on project. It offers strong value for the money, with an honest presentation and the kind of accessible pricing that makes ownership easy. A smart opportunity for anyone who wants maximum utility without a big upfront investment.",
      "price": 4995.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport or a great little project to tinker with. It\u2019s priced to make sense, has a lot of value for the money, and could be just the right fit for a first-time driver, commuter, or anyone who needs something without spending a fortune. If you want an honest car at an honest price, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project with strong enthusiast upside. Runs and drives, with a willing engine, good oil pressure behavior, and a drivetrain that still feels mechanically honest. Suspension, brakes, and cosmetics show age, but the car presents as a complete, usable platform for someone who wants a budget-friendly driver or restoration candidate. Straightforward layout makes it easy to wrench on, and it has the kind of analog feel and road presence that\u2019s getting harder to find. Not perfect, but a capable foundation with plenty of life left for the next owner.",
      "price": 7950.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Rough around the edges, but it gets the job done. Clean title. Cheap entry point. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with loads of personality, this car has the kind of honest, road-worn charm that turns the right buyer into an instant dreamer. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for a project, a dependable spare, or a budget-friendly set of wheels for someone who appreciates character over polish. There\u2019s a story in every panel and a sense of possibility in every drive\u2014an affordable chance to make it your own and enjoy a vehicle with grit, presence, and plenty of life left to give.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers affordable transportation with honest value for a buyer who appreciates a practical project or low-cost daily driver. A sensible option for someone seeking dependable basics at an accessible price point.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s best suited for someone handy, looking for a budget runabout, or wanting a project with potential. It\u2019s not perfect and shows its age, but it\u2019s a straightforward, affordable option from a seller who believes in being upfront. If you want something cheap with life left in it and don\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with strong bones and plenty of upside. Runs, drives, and offers a responsive powertrain feel with a chassis that still has usable life left. Cosmetic wear, age-related flaws, and general reconditioning needs are present, so it\u2019s best suited for someone who knows their way around maintenance or wants an affordable platform to sort and improve. A great chance to get into a capable car at an accessible price without paying cleaned-up retail.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
